{
  "texts": [
    "For configuration in the Lattice Estimator, we choose RC.MATZOV [MAT22] as the cost model in the classical setting.",
    "Note that the work by [MAT22] introduces two components: a refinement of the sieving cost and a dual attack strategy.",
    "The sieving cost improvement is generally accepted, and is integrated by default in the Lattice Estimator.",
    "However, the dual attack strategy, which is also integrated by default in the Estimator, has been subject to critique [DP23b].",
    "These critiques are not unique to [MAT22] but apply to a class of dual attacks employing FFT tricks, including e.g."
  ]
}